|MK0The Rift Duergar are a race of evil subterranean dwarves who have been
twisted by dark forces into hateful caricatures of surface dwarves. They are
short, stout and have hardy constitutions, enabling them to hold their
liquor and resist small amounts of magic and mental influence. Despite
being quite strong, Rift Duergar have problems balancing larger weapons
due to their stature.

